Key Points in Transition
------------------------

transition-property: all/font-size/background-color

transition-duration: 2s

transition-timing-function: ease-in/ease-out/ease/ease-in-out/linear/step-start/step-end

transtion-delay: 2s

transition: property-name | duration | timing-function | delay

transition: all 1s ease-in 0

