ANIMATIONS
----------

1. Create animation rules
2. Set Animation Properties

@keyframe animation_name1{
  from {
    transform: rotate(0);
    color: red;
    }
  to {
    transform: rotate(360deg);
    color: green
    }
}

animation-name: animation_name1;
animation-duration: 3s;
animation-timing-function: ease-in;
animation-delay: 1s;
animation-iteration-count: infinity
animation-direction: normal/reverse/alternate/alternate-re

animation: anim_name duration timing_function delay interation_count direction